Creating a landing page for a real estate website using Astro involves several components. Below is a production-ready Astro component named `Menu` along with a basic structure for the landing page including `Hero`, `Testimonials`, `Pricing`, and `Footer` sections. You can expand each section as needed.

First, ensure you have Astro installed. If not, you can set up a new Astro project using the following commands:

bash
npm create astro@latest
cd your-project-name
npm install


Now, let's create the `Menu` component and the landing page structure.

### `Menu.astro`


---
// src/components/Menu.astro
const menuItems = [
  { name: 'Home', href: '#' },
  { name: 'About', href: '#about' },
  { name: 'Testimonials', href: '#testimonials' },
  { name: 'Pricing', href: '#pricing' },
  { name: 'Contact', href: '#contact' },
];
---

<nav class="menu">
  <ul>
    {menuItems.map((item) => (
      <li>
        <a href={item.href}>{item.name}</a>
      </li>
    ))}
  </ul>
</nav>

<style>
  .menu {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: #333;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .menu ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .menu ul li a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .menu ul li a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>


### `Hero.astro`


---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section id="hero" class="hero">
  <h1>Find Your Dream Home</h1>
  <p>Discover the perfect property for you and your family.</p>
  <button>Get Started</button>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: url('/path-to-your-image.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
    color: white;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .hero button {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .hero button:hover {
    background-color: #0056b3;
  }
</style>


### `Testimonials.astro`


---
// src/components/Testimonials.astro
const testimonials = [
  { name: 'John Doe', text: 'Great service and fantastic properties!' },
  { name: 'Jane Smith', text: 'I found my dream home here. Thank you!' },
];
---

<section id="testimonials" class="testimonials">
  <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>
  <div class="testimonials-container">
    {testimonials.map((testimonial) => (
      <div class="testimonial">
        <p>"{testimonial.text}"</p>
        <h3>- {testimonial.name}</h3>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
  }
  .testimonials h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .testimonials-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .testimonial {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    max-width: 300px;
  }
  .testimonial p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .testimonial h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #007bff;
  }
</style>


### `Pricing.astro`


---
// src/components/Pricing.astro
const pricingPlans = [
  { name: 'Basic', price: '$99/month', features: ['Feature 1', 'Feature 2', 'Feature 3'] },
  { name: 'Standard', price: '$199/month', features: ['Feature 1', 'Feature 2', 'Feature 3', 'Feature 4'] },
  { name: 'Premium', price: '$299/month', features: ['Feature 1', 'Feature 2', 'Feature 3', 'Feature 4', 'Feature 5'] },
];
---

<section id="pricing" class="pricing">
  <h2>Our Pricing Plans</h2>
  <div class="pricing-container">
    {pricingPlans.map((plan) => (
      <div class="pricing-plan">
        <h3>{plan.name}</h3>
        <p class="price">{plan.price}</p>
        <ul>
          {plan.features.map((feature) => (
            <li>{feature}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <button>Choose Plan</button>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background-color: white;
  }
  .pricing h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .pricing-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .pricing-plan {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    max-width: 300px;
  }
  .pricing-plan h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .pricing-plan .price {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #007bff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .pricing-plan ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .pricing-plan ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .pricing-plan button {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .pricing-plan button:hover {
    background-color: #0056b3;
  }
</style>


